room_title: Escape room "Sabotage: Chattanooga 1944" by Time to Escape in Chattanooga
room_description: It is 1944, Chattanooga - during WWII, thousands of train cars loaded with troops or war supplies passed through Chattanooga. The FBI suspects a plot to sabotage the war effort is underway. Can you uncover the saboteur in time to help save the troops?
